==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiān líng líng, dì líng líng
===Phrase===
'''[[天]][[灵]][[灵]]，[[地]][[灵]][[灵]]'''
# a spell said by a wizzard or shaman (similar to [[abracadabra]])

